To build and install lgmon:

        ./autogen.sh --program-suffix=<Printer Model Name>
        make
        make install

To build and install lgmon with AUTOCONF

You can set the following <Printer Model Name>.
            ip2700
            mx340
            mx350
            mx870

Example for building the mx870 lgmon with the new automake and autoconf:
        ./autogen.sh --program-suffix=mx870
        make
        make install

